IO-BufferedSelect2 version 1.1
==============================

See POD in lib/IO/BufferedSelect2.pm

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Linux::Inotify2

